{
  "stem": "20035.4",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "We knew by having our job, the so-called Canadish group, the Canadian group, that dad and grandpa immediately went to gas chamber and crematorium.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "At least we hope it was the gas chamber and crematorium.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "But anyway, we knew exactly they went-- they went on the wrong side of the track.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So our aim, our duty, our what-- desire to live was to find out if mom is alive, how is she, and what she's doing.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And when we found this one up-- and as a matter, a couple of days later, once again through this rumor mill, even the barrack number was given to us, where she is.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She was in barrack 14.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And shamelessly, I went over to the SS guard, the same SS guard who-- who was quite nice.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I asked him the question, is there any way we can let mom know that we are alive and what-how and what?",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he just turned around, kicked me in the pants and told me to get back in-- into the line.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I got a healthy kick from him.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And didn't expect too much more.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Really didn't expect any miracle from him.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And a couple of days later, maybe a week later, on the morning when we were leaving, he selected out of the 100, 10 people, which included my brother and I.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And there was a pushcart there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You know, with the two big wheels and with some blankets, or some clothing on top of it.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he started to tell us oh, that SS guard took the rest of the 90 of them away to work.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And he took the 10 of us.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We pushed that cart.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And we had no idea where we are going, what are we doing.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
